s=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xvc1665703135585.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xvc1665703135585.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xvc1665703135585.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xvc1665703135585\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__uniname_406458\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of a component, instance, operation, parameter, entity, or entity\n      field.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__topic_d122477e1_d122478e1_d122479e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xvc1665703135585_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__codeblock_fvl_g22_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uniname (UHACThAny, intseqNr, intmaxLen, UCHAR*name);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__topic_d86717e1_d86718e1_d86719e1_d86720e1_d86721e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885866e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__parml_ewr_h22_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hAny</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle of an instance, operation, parameter, or entity.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the parameter or entity field.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">maxLen</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Maximum size of the name to be returned.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">name</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Requested name. This buffer must be at least as large as the value of\n                     <var class=\"keyword varname\">maxLen</var>. (Output).</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__topic_d86722e1_d86723e1_d86724e1_d86725e1_d86726e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885866e113\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by uniname</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">Success.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">-57</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">Instance was not found.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">-165</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">The supplied handle is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">-1203</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">The sequence number is out of range.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__1\">-1406</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xvc1665703135585__table_d14933e1_d14934e1_d14935e1__entry__2\">Memory could not be allocated or freed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__topic_d86727e1_d86728e1_d86729e1_d86730e1_d86731e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885866e192\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__topic_d86732e1_d86733e1_d86734e1_d86735e1_d86736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885866e204\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__p_d122510e1_d122511e1_d122512e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uniname</code> returns the name of an\n            instance, component, operation, parameter, or entity field, depending on the type of\n            handle that was supplied in <var class=\"keyword varname\">hAny</var>. For a parameter or entity field,\n            the sequence number must be supplied in parameter <var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var> (which must\n            be between 1 and the number of parameters or fields, inclusive).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__p_d122513e1_d122514e1_d122515e1\">When the supplied handle is an instance handle, you\n            can set <var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var> to 0 to get the instance name (if any), or to 1 to get\n            the name of the component.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__section_mbq_422_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885866e227\">Example:  uoprprms, uniname, uprmdir, and uprmtype</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following routine prints out a list of the parameters of an arbitrary\n            operation in an arbitrary component.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xvc1665703135585_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__codeblock_rkd_q22_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n\nchar *types[] = { \"Unknown\", \"String\", \"Boolean\", \"Numeric\", \"Float\", \"Date\", \"Time\",\n\"DateTime\",\"LinearDate\", \"LinearTime\", \"LinearDateTime\", \"Raw\", \"Image\", \"Entity\",\n\"Occurrence\", \"IncludedEntity\", \"Handle\" };\nchar *dires[] = { \"Unknown\", \"In\", \"Out\", \"InOut\" };\n\nvoid inspect_operation_params (char *svcname, char *oprname)\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn, hOp, hParm;\nlong i, nParams;\nint pType, pDir;\nchar name[1+UPRMNAMESIZE];\nchar* template1 = \" %3s %-20s %-20s %s\\n\";\nchar* template2 = \" %3d %-20s %-20s %s\\n\";\n\nueopen(&amp;hEnv);\nuinstnew(hEnv, (UCHAR*)svcname, 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, 0);\nuinstopr(hIn, (UCHAR*)oprname, 0, &amp;hOp);\nprintf(\"Parameters of operation %s in service %s:\\n\\n\", oprname, svcname);\nprintf(template1, \"Num\", \"Name \", \"Type \",\n\"Direction\");\nprintf(template1, \"===\", \"====================\", \"====================\",\n\"=========\");\n\nuoprprms(hOp, &amp;nParams);\nfor ( i=1; i&lt;=nParams; i++ )\n{\nuprmdir(hOp, i, &amp;pDir);\nuprmgeth(hOp, i, 0, &amp;hParm);\nuprmtype(hParm, &amp;pType);\nuniname(hOp, i, UPRMNAMESIZE, name);\n\nprintf(template2, i, name, types[pType], dires[pDir]);\n}\nprintf(\"\\n\");\n\nuinstdel(hIn, 0);\nufreeh(&amp;hOp);\nufreeh(&amp;hIn);\nufreeh(&amp;hEnv);\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Here is an example of output generated by this function:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xvc1665703135585_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xvc1665703135585__codeblock_sdm_s22_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Parameters of operation MYOP in service TESTSVC:\n\nNum Name Type Direction\n=== ==================== ==================== =========\n1 P1 Numeric In\n2 P2 String InOut\n3 P3 Date Out</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oud1665702693770.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uoprprms</a><p>Return the number of parameters in the specified operation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uniname Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the name of a component, instance, operation, parameter, entity, or entity field. Explain this code long uniname (UHACThAny, intseqNr, intmaxLen, UCHAR*name); Copy Parameters hAny Handle of an instance, operation, parameter, or entity. seqNr Sequence number of the parameter or entity field. maxLen Maximum size of the name to be returned. name Requested name. This buffer must be at least as large as the value of maxLen . (Output). Return Values Table 1. Values returned by uniname Value Meaning 0 Success. -57 Instance was not found. -165 The supplied handle is not valid. -1203 The sequence number is out of range. -1406 Memory could not be allocated or freed. Use Library: ucall Description uniname returns the name of an instance, component, operation, parameter, or entity field, depending on the type of handle that was supplied in hAny . For a parameter or entity field, the sequence number must be supplied in parameter seqNr (which must be between 1 and the number of parameters or fields, inclusive). When the supplied handle is an instance handle, you can set seqNr to 0 to get the instance name (if any), or to 1 to get the name of the component. Example: uoprprms, uniname, uprmdir, and uprmtype The following routine prints out a list of the parameters of an arbitrary operation in an arbitrary component. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> char *types[] = { \"Unknown\", \"String\", \"Boolean\", \"Numeric\", \"Float\", \"Date\", \"Time\", \"DateTime\",\"LinearDate\", \"LinearTime\", \"LinearDateTime\", \"Raw\", \"Image\", \"Entity\", \"Occurrence\", \"IncludedEntity\", \"Handle\" }; char *dires[] = { \"Unknown\", \"In\", \"Out\", \"InOut\" }; void inspect_operation_params (char *svcname, char *oprname) { UHACT hEnv, hIn, hOp, hParm; long i, nParams; int pType, pDir; char name[1+UPRMNAMESIZE]; char* template1 = \" %3s %-20s %-20s %s\\n\"; char* template2 = \" %3d %-20s %-20s %s\\n\"; ueopen(&hEnv); uinstnew(hEnv, (UCHAR*)svcname, 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, 0); uinstopr(hIn, (UCHAR*)oprname, 0, &hOp); printf(\"Parameters of operation %s in service %s:\\n\\n\", oprname, svcname); printf(template1, \"Num\", \"Name \", \"Type \", \"Direction\"); printf(template1, \"===\", \"====================\", \"====================\", \"=========\"); uoprprms(hOp, &nParams); for ( i=1; i<=nParams; i++ ) { uprmdir(hOp, i, &pDir); uprmgeth(hOp, i, 0, &hParm); uprmtype(hParm, &pType); uniname(hOp, i, UPRMNAMESIZE, name); printf(template2, i, name, types[pType], dires[pDir]); } printf(\"\\n\"); uinstdel(hIn, 0); ufreeh(&hOp); ufreeh(&hIn); ufreeh(&hEnv); } Copy Here is an example of output generated by this function: Explain this code Parameters of operation MYOP in service TESTSVC: Num Name Type Direction === ==================== ==================== ========= 1 P1 Numeric In 2 P2 String InOut 3 P3 Date Out Copy Related Links uoprprms Return the number of parameters in the specified operation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}